OL,3,CBreakdown surge sparks Easter travel
OL,4,Cwarning for London motorists
OL,6,FAlmost half of drivers in the capital
OL,7,Fsay their breakdowns could have been
OL,8,Favoided through quick, basic checks.
OL,10,FThe National Highway is encouraging
OL,11,Fdrivers to follow 'T.R.I.P' in the
OL,12,Fdays before a long journey.
OL,14,FTop-up- Fuel or electric charge, oil
OL,15,Fand screen wash.
OL,17,FRest- Take a minimum 15minute break
OL,18,Fevery two hours behind the wheel to
OL,19,Favoid fatigue and get a good night's
OL,20,Frest before travelling.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
